Anan Says Lockerbie Case "on Way to Settlement" &HT; Urgent

Abu Dhabi 12-6 (AFP) - United Nations Secretary-General, Kofi Anan, informed the American Secretary of State, Madeleine Albright, that the Lockerbie case is "on its way to settlement", according to a spokesman for the international organization.
